Enterprise Networking and Communications Worldwide
</a>
</font>
  </td>
 </tr>

 <tr>
  <td class="contentText">
Gartner's coverage of enterprise networking and communications encompasses integration tools and standards supporting data transfer and management reporting across multiple applications. It covers the size, growth potential, key technologies, trends and vendor strategies for products that manage voice traffic and "converged" platforms handling both simultaneously. Topics covered include: 

<ul>
 <li /> Hubs, routers and switches supporting distributed enterprises 
 <li /> Home-networking products and applications 
 <li /> Contact center applications 
 <li /> Remote-access devices 
 <li /> Network management tools and protocols 
 <li /> Distribution channels supporting converged networks 
</ul>
  </td>
 </tr>
 



