Covers the dynamics of the public network market for next-generation and traditional equipment used by telecommunications service providers. Topics covered include: 

<ul>
 <li /> Optical transmission and "switching" 
 <li /> Switching systems and lines 
 <li /> Soft switches 
 <li /> Asynchronous transfer mode (ATM) switches and Internet protocol (IP) core routers 
 <li /> Media gateways and controllers 
 <li /> Intelligent network/advanced intelligent network (IN/AIN) equipment 
 <li /> Access infrastructure equipment 
 <li /> Wireless infrastructure equipment
</ul>
